Library Manager is a free software visual tool for managing XBMC own media
library. Currently it has the following features:
* Move movie files across diferent paths preserving database integrity as well
  the related thumbnails images.

Limitations:
* Only works with filesystem sources. Thats it, SMB, UPnP and other source types
  that XBMC can handle, currently, are NOT supported by this addon.

INSTALL
=======
1. Download a zipped package from here: 
    https://github.com/albertfc/XBMC-Library-Manager/zipball/master

2. Go to: System > Add-ons > Install from zip file and select previously
   downloaded file.

EXECUTE
=======
1. Go to: Programs > Library Manager
  
